                    <comment id="12983252" author="mikemccand" created="Tue, 18 Jan 2011 16:32:57 +0000"  >&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;So I guess all that&apos;s needed is to deprecate IW.getReader(int) on 3x and remove from trunk?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

